Body:
async with stream_from_subscription_transform(((x, 10) for x in [0, 0, 0, 0,
    1, 0, 1, 1, 0, None, None, None, None]), granularity_timeout=31) as s:
    await s.expect_after(10, 0)
    await trio.sleep(35)
    await s.expect_after(0, 0)
    await s.expect_after(5, 1)
    await trio.sleep(25)
    await s.expect_after(6, 1)
    await s.expect_after(9, 0)
    await s.expect_exit_after(40)
pytest.mark.trio
